<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Shimmor</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-01-26 03:00:37</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>This is found in Rathe Mountains near the Paladin camp.  Trin Rhilstone(SP?) is the rare spawn that has it.  He is an Erudite Paladin.  This is his common drop the rare drop is the man-o-war hammer.  Because of the way Veriant has the encounter tables set up you will have to kill newbie critters for a couple of hours to get him to spawn.  He spawned in a couple different locations next to the camp so his spawning point is somewhat random also.  The hood is a very nice item and has the look of patchwork which is very nice for enchanters.  Good Luck.   </font></td></tr></table>
