<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Quid Rilestone is his name, he poped for me  between the Paladin camp and Orc camp. Hes in black and grey clothing and spawned next to the Orc camp just off the wooden post.<BR>
This took around 6hrs of killing the spawn spots on top, between and around the Paladin/Orc camps including the Orcs. Not only is this a very nice cha item it adds a 3ft or so swaying tail to your elemental illusions and looks different depending on what race illusion you use. Good Luck </font></td></tr></table>
